{"id":827099058,"question_id":10,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 7 months","timestamp":1666330189,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"86 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/827099058/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Regular Expression Matching","memory":"41.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    \n    int len_s;\n    int len_p;\n    String s;\n    String p;\n    public boolean isMatch(String s, String p) {\n        \n        this.s=s;\n        this.p=p;\n        len_s = s.length();\n        len_p = p.length();\n        \n        return dfs(0,0);\n        \n        \n    }\n    \n    \n    private boolean dfs(int i, int j){\n        if(i>=len_s && j>=len_p)\n            return true;\n        \n        if(j>=len_p)\n            return false;\n        \n        boolean match = i<len_s && (s.charAt(i)==p.charAt(j) || p.charAt(j)=='.');\n        if(j+1<len_p && p.charAt(j+1)=='*'){\n            return (match && dfs(i+1, j)) || dfs(i, j+2);\n        }\n        \n        if( match && dfs(i+1, j+1))\n            return true;\n        \n    \n        return false;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"regular-expression-matching","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
